{"tid":320984,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"雞，全世界都係雞","createTime":"2017-07-14T02:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T03:21:09.000Z","uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe37126e6633d47d135635c9bc33c54ca9b2716","tid":320984,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T02:33:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.style.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E8%AC%9B%E6%97%A5%E5%A9%9A%E5%BE%8C5%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%80%E6%98%93%E5%87%BA%E8%BB%8C-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%96%E9%81%87%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA%E6%80%A7-081223119.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.style.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25AC%259B%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A9%259A%25E5%25BE%258C5%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2598%2593%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25BB%258C-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%2581%2587%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2580%25A7-081223119.html&d=%2BO3k%2BPpaLnRfGuh6YzXbMAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=09dd644c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.style.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E8%AC%9B%E6%97%A5%E5%A9%9A%E5%BE%8C5%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%80%E6%98%93%E5%87%BA%E8%BB%8C-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%96%E9%81%87%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA%E6%80%A7-081223119.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港女講日：婚後5年最易出軌 日本女人外遇因為性？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男人出軌，可以冇任何原因，可以純粹為咗貪心、刺激、咸濕而出軌。相反，女人出軌，多數係因為婚姻關係唔美滿，逼不得已先俾綠帽老公戴。日本人妻外遇比例向來高，《週刊FLASH》最近訪問100位有偷食經驗嘅人妻，發現好多人妻婚後最易就係同上司發生婚外情！<br />\n問起外遇對象，差唔多一半人妻與上司搭上(48%)!其次係朋友(14%)、同學(11%)、被人搭訕(9%)及同事(5%)。至於外遇維持咗幾耐，最多通常係半年至1年。<br />\n被問到發生性行為次數，28%人妻承認每2至3星期做愛一次，1星期一次有19%，幾日一次都有15%，值得留意就係，居然有88%坦承同外遇對象做愛舒服過同老公!睇嚟性方面得唔到滿足，係日本人妻偷食最大主因!<br />\n<br />\n另一個原因，係令佢哋搵返戀愛感覺！一名38歲人妻表示，某次聚會上發現老細好肯聽佢呻，而且仲主動幫佢解決問題，同佢老公完全唔同!飲到醉醉哋，老細仲「嘴對嘴」餵佢飲水，覺得老細好溫柔好關心佢，於是開始同對方幽會，甚至喺茶水間、會議室、廁所發生關係。<br />\n曾輔導超過1,000人戀愛心理嘅木田真也表示，結婚5年以上嘅女人最有可能外遇，因為仔女開始大唔駛花大多心機及時間湊，同時開始對婚姻冇哂新鮮感。其中一位41歲結婚8年嘅家庭主婦，當小朋友讀小學後多咗時間，因為想修身成日去做gym，咁就搭上咗健身教練喇!"},{"pid":"d93e9af564e8d588a96b82f501895a9a34385a52","tid":320984,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T02:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc7afa8df153e7dbf0573f8db284abf55b64b50","tid":320984,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T02:52:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74da1122de0a6a481fc0b6641a231d98e0bb0ff6","tid":320984,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T02:52:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33327cc129c4fa92aa45da78eaba233248a6eb66","tid":320984,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T03:21:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/105223_365e931022f7c7c7ee95bc9e47e1bba3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F105223_365e931022f7c7c7ee95bc9e47e1bba3.jpg&h=bdc64065&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}